title: Osagashi no Hatsukoi Aite wa Tabun Watashi desu, to wa Totemo Ienai.: Toubou Shita Moto Seijo, Mofumofu wo Kojiraseta Seinen to Saikai Suru
altTitle: お探しの初恋相手はたぶん私です、とはとても言えない。～逃亡した元聖女、もふもふをこじらせた青年と再会する～
I can't say that I'm the first love you've been looking for. ~I'm the former saint on the run, reunited with a man who loves fluff
